<div id="tmap-code" class="section level2">
<h2>Tmap code</h2>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-1" title="1">dataCatchment &lt;-<span class="st">  </span><span class="kw">dbReadTable</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-2" title="2">  con,  </a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-3" title="3">  <span class="st">&quot;v_abundance&quot;</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-4" title="4">) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span><span class="st"> </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-5" title="5"><span class="st">  </span><span class="kw">inner_join</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-6" title="6">    <span class="kw">tribble</span>(<span class="op">~</span>abundance_level_id, <span class="op">~</span>abundance_interpretation,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-7" title="7">            <span class="dv">1</span>, <span class="st">&#39;Not recorded in the period&#39;</span>,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-8" title="8">            <span class="dv">2</span>, <span class="st">&#39;Occasional vagrants&#39;</span>,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-9" title="9">            <span class="dv">3</span>, <span class="st">&#39;Functional populations&#39;</span>,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-10" title="10">            <span class="dv">4</span>, <span class="st">&#39;Abundant functional populations&#39;</span>) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span><span class="st"> </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-11" title="11"><span class="st">      </span><span class="kw">mutate</span>(<span class="dt">abundance_interpretation =</span> <span class="kw">factor</span>(abundance_interpretation,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-12" title="12">                                               <span class="dt">levels =</span> .<span class="op">$</span>abundance_interpretation)), </a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-13" title="13">    <span class="dt">by =</span> <span class="st">&quot;abundance_level_id&quot;</span>)</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-14" title="14"></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-15" title="15">catchment_geom &lt;-<span class="st"> </span><span class="kw">st_read</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-16" title="16">  con, </a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-17" title="17">  <span class="dt">query =</span>   <span class="st">&quot;SELECT * FROM diadesatlas.v_basin vb&quot;</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-18" title="18">) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-19" title="19"><span class="st">  </span>rmapshaper<span class="op">::</span><span class="kw">ms_simplify</span>()</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-20" title="20"></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-21" title="21">dataALL &lt;-<span class="st"> </span><span class="kw">dbGetQuery</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-22" title="22">  con, </a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-23" title="23">  <span class="st">&quot;SELECT * from diadesatlas.v_species_ices_occurence vsio &quot;</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-24" title="24">) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span><span class="st"> </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-25" title="25"><span class="st">  </span><span class="co">#tibble() %&gt;% </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-26" title="26"><span class="st">  </span><span class="kw">mutate</span>(<span class="dt">nb_occurence =</span> <span class="kw">as.integer</span>(nb_occurence))</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-27" title="27"></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-28" title="28">ices_geom &lt;-<span class="st"> </span><span class="kw">st_read</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-29" title="29">  con, </a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-30" title="30">  <span class="dt">query =</span> <span class="st">&quot;SELECT * FROM diadesatlas.v_ices_geom;&quot;</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-31" title="31">) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span><span class="st"> </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-32" title="32"><span class="st">  </span><span class="kw">st_transform</span>(<span class="st">&quot;+proj=eqearth +wktext&quot;</span>) <span class="op">%&gt;%</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-33" title="33"><span class="st">  </span>rmapshaper<span class="op">::</span><span class="kw">ms_simplify</span>()</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-34" title="34"></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-35" title="35"></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-36" title="36"><span class="co"># </span><span class="al">NOTE</span><span class="co">: the species are passed with the latin name in the foreground. </span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-37" title="37"><span class="co"># In the front of the app, the user will have to select an english/french name</span></a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-38" title="38"><span class="kw">tm_draw</span>(</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-39" title="39">  <span class="dt">species_latin_name =</span> <span class="st">&quot;Salmo trutta&quot;</span>,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-40" title="40">  <span class="dt">spatial_type =</span> <span class="st">&#39;rectangle&#39;</span>,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-41" title="41">  <span class="dt">con =</span> con,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-42" title="42">  <span class="dt">dataCatchment =</span> dataCatchment,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-43" title="43">  <span class="dt">catchment_geom =</span> catchment_geom,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-44" title="44">  <span class="dt">dataALL =</span> dataALL,</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-45" title="45">  <span class="dt">ices_geom =</span> ices_geom</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-46" title="46">)</a>
<a class="sourceLine" id="cb4-47" title="47"><span class="co">#&gt; Some legend labels were too wide. These labels have been resized to 0.25. Increase legend.width (argument of tm_layout) to make the legend wider and therefore the labels larger.</span></a></code></pre></div>
